  <title>Supported file formats</title>

  <p>File formats displayed by <app>Videos</app> depend on <gui>GStreamer</gui>
  plugins. Install plugin packages you need:</p>

  <list>
    <item>
      <p>The basic and essential plugin for GStreamer is
      <code>gst-plugins-base</code>.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>The plugin for most open formts is <code>gst-plugins-good</code>.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>The plugins needed to play DVDs are <code>gst-plugins-ugly</code> and
      <code>gst-plugins-bad</code>.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>The plugin, which contains all the basic decoders for popular codecs is
      <code>gst-ffmpeg</code>.</p>
    </item>
  </list>

